attempt to download all the available PDF versions of the articles (see Figure 2).  As you can see from the Figure, if the article isn’t available, PaperFetch lets you know.\r\n\r\nPlease note that a Java install is required, as well as an internet connection to PubMed.\r\n\r\nA 5-day trial for Windows or MacOS is available.  The software can be purchased by credit card or via PayPal for $21.\r\n\r\nPaperFetch is a very straightforward application.  For those that use PubMed extensively, the tool may provide some significant efficiencies.   The 5-day trial should be more than sufficient to give the application a try.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Test Brief Review','','draft','open','open','','','','','2014-10-23 15:16:09','2014-10-23 15:16:09','',0,'http://172.16.100.211/wordpress/?p=1918',0,'post','',0),(1919,1,'2014-10-23 14:41:28','2014-10-23 14:41:28','','Test Brief Review','','inherit','open','open','','1918-revision-v1','','','2014-10-23 14:41:28','2014-10-23 14:41:28','',1918,'http://172.16.100.211/wordpress/?p=1919',0,'revision','',0),(1920,1,'2014-10-23 14:42:11','2014-10-23 14:42:11','xcxc','Test Brief Review','','inherit','open','open','','1918-revision-v1','','','2014-10-23 14:42:11','2014-10-23 14:42:11','',1918,'http://172.16.100.211/wordpress/?p=1920',0,'revision','',0),(1921,1,'2014-10-23 14:43:28','2014-10-23 14:43:28','[inpost_fancy thumb_width=\"200\" thumb_height=\"200\" post_id=\"1918\" thumb_margin_left=\"0\" thumb_margin_bottom=\"0\" thumb_border_radius=\"2\" thumb_shadow=\"0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)\" id=\"\" random=\"0\" group=\"0\" border=\"\" show_in_popup=\"0\" album_cover=\"\" album_cover_width=\"200\" album_cover_height=\"200\" popup_width=\"800\" popup_max_height=\"600\" popup_title=\"Gallery\" type=\"fancy\" sc_id=\"sc1414075406316\"]','Test Brief Review','','inherit','open','open','','1918-revision-v1','','','2014-10-23 14:43:28','2014-10-23 14:43:28','',1918,'http://172.16.100.211/wordpress/?p=1921',0,'revision','',0),(1922,1,'2014-10-23 14:44